Panhandle Eastern Corp's Trunkline GasCo pipeline subsidiary said it is reducing the commoditycomponent of its wholesale natural gas rate four pct, effectiveimmediately.    In a filing with the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission,Trunkline said, it is reducing its commodity rate -- theportion of the total rate based on the price of gas -- to 2.58dlrs per mln Btu from 2.69 dlrs per mln Btu.    The company said the lower rate results from a reduction inthe average price the pipeline is paying for gas, adding thisreflects contract reformation agreemats with producers. Reuter&#3;